    <url>/2024/12/16/SDU-carpet-addition%E8%A7%84%E5%88%99/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="SDUcarpet规则"><a href="#SDUcarpet规则" class="headerlink" title="SDUcarpet规则"></a>SDUcarpet规则</h2><hr><h3 id="brittleDeepSlate"><a href="#brittleDeepSlate" class="headerlink" title="brittleDeepSlate"></a>brittleDeepSlate</h3><hr><p>If enable,deepSlate’s hardness will be change to 1.6  </p><ul><li>Type: Boolean  </li><li>Default value: false  </li><li>Allowed options: true, false  </li><li>Categories: SDU</li></ul><h3 id="armorStandIgnoreShulkerDamage"><a href="#armorStandIgnoreShulkerDamage" class="headerlink" title="armorStandIgnoreShulkerDamage"></a>armorStandIgnoreShulkerDamage</h3><hr><p>Shulkerbullet will not hurt ArmorStand.</p><ul><li>Type: Boolean</li><li>Default value: false</li><li>Allowed options: true, false</li><li>Categories: SDU</li></ul><h3 id="skipCropLightCheck"><a href="#skipCropLightCheck" class="headerlink" title="skipCropLightCheck"></a>skipCropLightCheck</h3>]]></content>
    
    
    
